<br>
    Soloing a Rockfiend is problematic (nearly impossible) below level 56 and is a huge mana drain 56+.  They sometimes drop a Shiny Granite Ball or Granite Chips, or in one case, one of each.<br>
<br>
    Shissar Stalkers, skeletons, and even Rockfiends can sometimes see invis, so the zone isn't 100% safe with invis up.<br>
<br>
    I usually camp on the wall near the Mons Letalis zone tunnel.  Single-pulling is not too difficult, but you need to be aware that ghosting is very very common in this zone, so mobs aren't always where they seem to be.  Just practice a little patience, and pull with a fast casting nuke.  The wandering mobs path pretty close to the Mons tunnel, meaning you will sooner or later see a Shissar Stalker alone and in pulling distance.  The ratio of Stalker kills to the Organ drops is perhaps 10:1.  Maybe a little worse than that.<br>
<br>
